      "span_text": "106 A dose- 95 or surgical gastric bypass.  64 Results for liposuction are contradictory: Although one such study 99 resulting in a mean weight loss of 3 kg found concentrations of IL-6, IL-18, TNF-α and CRP to be reduced after a 6-month period of weight stability, another 96 in which fat mass was reduced by 9.8 kg on average found IL-6, TNF-α and CRP concentrations to be unaltered 10-12 weeks after the surgery.",
